Filming began in November 1997. Shah Rukh Khan also shot for Kuch Kuch Hota Hai simultaneously. Mani Ratnam had initially cast Kajol in the lead female role, though Manisha Koirala later replaced her.Likewise, Simran was cast in a secondary lead role and opted out of other projects to accommodate the film. She later turned down the film citing that the role was too small and would affect her work in the Tamil and Telugu cinema industries. Preity Zinta was later brought in to replace her.
